<br />\n【投訴警察制度行之有效？】<br />\n現實係...<br />\n2011-2018年期間，合共有2119項投訴警察毆打的指控，當中只有2宗獲「證明屬實」，投訴成功率是0.09%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家明的"},{"pid":"04647f989f13206e2b172389fab35cd5b17f0fb6","tid":2235200,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"周浩X咁支持嗰個話斬人係高尚情操嘅法官，咁佢係咪鼓勵香港人去進行呢啲咁暴力嘅罪行"},{"pid":"439d5d86929d0e39bf620d92ee16f51e8fe7ad5d","tid":2235200,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 投訴師好有用, 無成本功效大, 未做過又點知<br />\n<br />\n現實: 何俊堯早前處理6宗審訊的投訴均不成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0364098a3a89a4240907cb2570d7679d70a76c9","tid":2235200,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">【德國戰線聯署】絲打拍埋片教你點簽！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2231070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2231070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國政府官方聯署：夠數德國就必須喺國會討論制裁中國<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229100</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人真係咁撚懶？ 德國聯署講到明夠數開會都唔做？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2231699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2231699</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8edb8702847dd696e4cd69933cde469df1e85ae6","tid":2235200,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fed77604f8a7bb1e61220b22147d90774c76969","tid":2235200,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"係你自己攞黎，而家審親就要贏呀，咁唔駛審啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"yep"},{"pid":"ae6ee54fc8f8a0a5d02dd1f4c495220e81ff47ce","tid":2235200,"uid":2